Fetch Dataset A (Futures Only): Use your original URL (72hh-3qpy).
Fetch Dataset B (Combined): Use the new URL above (kh3c-gbw2).
Join the Data: Merge the two JSON responses on the exact same report_date_as_yyyy_mm_dd.
Do the Math: For every single column (Longs, Shorts, Spreads) inside Producer, Swap Dealer, Managed Money, etc., simply subtract Dataset A from Dataset B.
